80 Grey Street comprises a functional office/warehouse benefiting from direct access to the Tonkin Highway/Collier Road interchange.  The warehouse is made up of three adjoining bays, each with independent full height roller door access allowing for “strata type” storage or larger scale single warehouse use suitable for transport and logistics operators. 

Building Scenario 1:
•	Office: 200sqm + Warehouse: 2,190sqm

Building Scenario 2:
•	Office: 200sqm + Warehouse: 1,730sqm

Key Features:

•	Land Area: 4,620sqm*
•	Office: 200sqm*
•	Warehouse: 2,190sqm*
•	High Truss Warehouse
•	Flexible lease terms
•	Secure site with perimeter fencing
•	500m* to Tonkin Highway/Collier Road interchange
•	25 Parking Bays plus additional street front parking
•	Proximity to Perth CBD & Perth Airport

This cost-effective warehouse facility is ideal for Transport & logistics businesses servicing Perth’s Northern and Eastern suburbs.

For more information or to book a viewing, contact one of the exclusive leasing agents.

*approx.

25 Jackson Street comprises a rare, 2.32Ha site improved with 3,094sqm* of office/warehouse improvements and 11,000sqm* of newly laid asphalt hardstand.  The property is strategically located within proximity to the recently completed Collier Road/Tonkin Highway interchange being just 8.5km* north east of the Perth CBD and 4km* north west of the Perth domestic airport making this a prime site for a major transport and logistics operator.

The owner is also willing to consider purpose built development options for suitable, long term tenants.

KEY FEATURES:
• Office: 235 sqm*
• Warehouse 1: 862 sqm*
• Warehouse 2: 1,994 sqm*
• Recently re-cladded building elevations
• Additional access point from Alice Street
• Situated on the 36.5m oversized restricted access network
• Proximity to Tonkin Highway/Collier Road Interchange
• Negotiable lease terms
• Purpose built options considered

25 Jackson Street is priced at a competitive hardstand rate with all building included.  For further information or to arrange a viewing please contact the exclusive leasing agents.

*Approx

CBRE is proud to offer the opportunity to acquire one of Bassendean's premier industrial properties.

184 Railway Parade has street frontage and access to Railway Parade with Perth CBD 10km* to the west.

Bassendean is a well established industrial area that continues to remain tightly held with the majority of business located within the suburb.

Situated on the 41,491sqm* site is a two level office building with a floor area of 5,670sqm*.

The facility incorporates a centrally located atrium/foyer which incorporates a front reception and walkways leading to 2 staircases, a modern lift servicing the first floor and a large staff cafe/breakout room. The offices have a good standard of fit out and finish with extensive uses of office cubicles and enclosed offices. Separate recently refurbished male and female toilets and kitchenette facilities area provided on both levels.

The office building is freestanding, has full height glass elevations and is set amongst extensive landscaped lawn and garden areas. There are three main car park areas, the first being situated directly in front of the office building providing staff and visitor open car bays.

To the side and rear of the office building are two (2) further good size open bitumen paved car park areas.

NABERS rating exempt.
